{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, it can distinguish the difference between the outcome of HbA1c and the drop of HbA1c.",
    "These properties allow GPT to be further developed into a powerful and systematic tool to evaluate the performance of complex information extraction.However, it is important to acknowledge several limitations in this study.",
    "First, while covering a wide range of medical domains, the labeled ground truth represents the assessment level of human evaluators.",
    "It may not necessarily serve as the golden standard due to a lack of domain knowledge.",
    "As a result, the performance of GPTs could be underestimated."
  ]
}